    "description": "Grow your career with Reliance Footprint! We are hiring a Department Manager for our Allahabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Reliance Footprint:\nReliance Footprint is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Reliance Footprint!",
